headline: Otis Wins Silver Award for Outstanding Safety Performance at SBS Transit Safe Business Partner Awards 2025
summary: Otis has been honored with a Silver Award at the SBS Transit Safe Business Partner Awards 2025, recognizing strong safety performance while operating on SBS Transit premises. Otis Worldwide Corporation (NYSE: OTIS) is the world's leading elevator and escalator manufacturing, installation and service company.
